<div class="page-header">
  <div class="eyebrow">Neurology · CNS Pathophysiology</div>
  <h1>The Eye is <em>CNS</em></h1>
  <div class="header-meta">
    <span class="pill teal">Embryology</span>
    <span class="pill hot">Clinical Implications</span>
